properties.Name: ChannelApplicableTax
properties.Description: The tax(es) that are applicable to transactions involving the product.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: TaxId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Tax.

Columns.Name: TaxExemptIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the tax is exempt for the channel and does not need to be collected.

Columns.Name: TaxApplicableToStoreIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the tax is applicable to the store and needs to be collected and remitted to the appropriate authorities.

Columns.Name: TaxIncludedInPriceIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the tax is already included in the product list price or whether it needs to be added during the transaction.
